cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.HC 

The paper is about facial expression recognition using Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs), which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses algorithmic differences and performance impact, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The application of facial expression recognition has implications for multimedia (cs.MM) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
